         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">29/1/62. ¶ My dear Dr Macadam. ¶  ¶ I beg to enclose this letter ¶ R. Dickson to M, 28 January 1862. ¶  ¶ with a request to learn whether Mr Dickson was instructed by you to write to me the byefollowi...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">62.01.29</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To John Macadam</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MS 13071 Royal Society of Victoria Exploration Committee records, box 2078/3, La Trobe Australian Manuscripts Collection, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS black-edged.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M's sister, Bertha Doughty, died on 7 September 1861.</p>
               </note>29/1/62.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Dr Macadam.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I beg to enclose this letter<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>R. Dickson to M, 28 January 1862.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>with a request to learn whether Mr Dickson was instructed by you to write to me the byefollowing letter. I object not only to the uncourteous tone but also to the request itself, in as much as he refers to the transcripts of the Exploration journals, which were not ordered by the Exploration Committee to be returned from the Offices of the daily papers. I undertook by special desire of the Explor. Committee the transcription<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">and returned the original journals</hi>
               </seg>, which are consequently available. If the latter had been taken to the journal offices it would be quite right to ask for their restoration, altho' I would not [even] individually be responsible for them, as the copies were not on my own idea but by order of the Chairman of the Expl Committee forwarded by myself to the newspapers Offices.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I cannot but think that you have been misinformed in the matter, as I can not anticipate that you would have found reason to depart from your usual urbanity in this instance</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Believe me</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>dear Dr Macadam</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your very truly</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
